# Validation

## Purpose

No completion claims without evidence.

## Rules

- Do not declare done without verification evidence
- Do not claim ChatGPT Search lift without registered observation + causal setup
- Do not skip critical quality gates
- Prefer contract tests before implementation expansion
- Independent critic / second pass for release-affecting changes

## Bootstrap validation checklist

1. Requested dirs/files exist
2. Spec originals unchanged
3. No application implementation code
4. No `package.json` / `pyproject.toml` / `Dockerfile` (until explicitly allowed)
5. No secrets
6. Cursor allow/deny documented
7. Provider adapter boundaries separated
8. Deployment profiles separated
9. Tenant-aware principles documented
10. Service boundaries traceable to specs
11. Protected paths defined
12. No git commit/push/merge by agent unless user asked

## Status

CONFIRMED
